## Markdown-it-attributes

Add classes, identifiers and attributes to your markdown with {.class #identifier attr=value attr2="spaced value"} curly brackets

<include src="outputBox.md" boilerplate >
<span id="markdown-it-attributes">

```
# header {.style-me}
paragraph {data-toggle=modal}
```
</span>
<span id="output">

```
<h1 class="style-me">header</h1>
<p data-toggle="modal">paragraph</p>
```
</span>
